    "created_at": "2015-07-14T08:28:25Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-14T08:28:25Z",
    "body": "That would be great. It would also leave the choice up to the developer, what they want the left click to do. I know some people like to use the left click to toggle the status and then use the right click to open the menu.\n"
